WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:01.101
So hear the word of the Lord.

00:02.883 --> 00:16.416
So all the generations from Abraham to David were 14 generations and from David to the deportation to Babylon 14 generations and from the deportation to Babylon to the Christ 14 generations.

00:17.837 --> 00:26.866
Now the birth of Christ took place in this way when his mother Mary had been betrothed to Joseph before they came together.

00:27.234 --> 00:30.078
She was found to be with child from the Holy Spirit.

00:31.380 --> 00:37.469
And her husband Joseph, being a just man and unwilling to put her to shame, resolved to divorce her quietly.

00:38.811 --> 00:47.763
But as he considered those things, behold an angel of the Lord appeared to him in a dream saying, Joseph, son of David, do not fear to take Mary as your wife.

00:48.625 --> 00:51.949
For that which is conceived in her is from the Holy Spirit.

00:51.969 --> 00:55.154
She will bear a son and you shall call his name Jesus.

00:55.842 --> 00:57.904
for he will save his people from their sins.

00:59.486 --> 01:11.037
And this took, all this took place to fulfill what the Lord had spoken by the prophet, but hold the virgin, so conceive and bear a son, and they shall call his name Emmanuel, which means God with us.

01:12.098 --> 01:24.690
When Joseph awoke from sleep, he did not, he did as the angel of the Lord commanded him, he took his wife, but knew her not until she had given birth to a son, and he called his name Jesus.

01:25.666 --> 01:30.491
The grass weathers and the flowers fade, but the word of our God will stand forever.

01:30.792 --> 01:31.713
Amen, you may be seated.

01:33.435 --> 01:33.935
Pray with me.

01:40.843 --> 01:42.685
Holy Father, we give you thanks for your word.

01:44.467 --> 01:54.098
Your word which took on flesh, what an amazing, incomprehensible miracle this is as we stare

01:54.274 --> 01:55.796
deeply at these mysteries.

01:58.840 --> 02:05.931
But you give us, ah, you give us imagination to just glimmer, even just a hint of what this means.

02:05.991 --> 02:10.737
And may you inspire and strengthen our hope.

02:12.380 --> 02:16.065
But you do this by the power of your spirit, working in and through your word this morning.

02:16.426 --> 02:16.786
Amen.

02:19.042 --> 02:24.387
You know, the other day when I was driving to Costco, I noticed something that I've never really noticed before.

02:24.427 --> 02:28.612
The giant billboard that's got like the lottery numbers and what you can win.

02:28.672 --> 02:31.915
And the one that stood out to me is this is, listen, I'm not a gambler.

02:31.935 --> 02:33.316
I'm not trying to promote this.

02:33.336 --> 02:34.457
It's just an illustration, all right?

02:34.938 --> 02:35.638
It was a power ball.

02:35.659 --> 02:38.361
And the power ball number is like close to a billion dollars.

02:39.022 --> 02:41.484
And I was like, oh, maybe I'd buy a ticket for a billion dollars.

02:42.165 --> 02:47.250
And then I started going through my mind, thinking about what would I do?

02:47.650 --> 02:50.694
I heard the voice of my father's like, well, you know, you only get like half of that.

02:50.714 --> 02:53.056
And I was like, well, I could deal with half a billion.

02:53.377 --> 02:54.778
It's 500 million.

02:55.119 --> 02:56.560
Still a good amount to play with.

02:57.081 --> 03:02.627
And so in my head, I went to this like, honestly, this was probably maybe six to 10 hours, but I wish I went through this.

03:03.448 --> 03:06.812
I was working to, I'm sure I was, I wasn't like unproductive during this time.

03:06.852 --> 03:09.475
In the back of my mind, I was just thinking, well, what would I do with that money?

03:10.056 --> 03:11.558
And let me just tell you, I did some really cool stuff.

03:11.578 --> 03:12.799
I basically bought Yakima.

03:13.380 --> 03:15.442
This carpet got replaced.

03:15.970 --> 03:18.654
You know, it's awesome.

03:18.674 --> 03:20.818
It was a very fun, fun moment for me.

03:21.319 --> 03:25.506
And there's a word for that, but you call that kind of thing wishful thinking, right?

03:25.526 --> 03:30.273
It's when you're daydreaming about something awesome.

03:31.255 --> 03:32.277
