03:32.858 --> 03:42.834
Listen, you know it probably won't happen, but you're okay with that, because you can just live there for a moment in your mind, and there's something amazing about that.

03:42.914 --> 03:49.540
And then real life drags you back down and you got bills to pay and you don't have 500 million in your bank to pay for those bills anymore.

03:49.821 --> 03:50.982
And it's like, oh, that's a bummer.

03:51.422 --> 03:52.804
