04:04.215 --> 04:05.156
It was too disappointed.

04:05.536 --> 04:07.358
If it doesn't happen, it doesn't ruin your life.

04:07.738 --> 04:11.602
Because it can't carry the weight of your hope.

04:12.194 --> 04:20.984
And I wonder though, if for a lot of us, the difference between hope and wishful thinking is not that far away from each other.

04:22.245 --> 04:29.573
Where hope is maybe a step further where hope says, you know, it's just a high likelihood of this coming true.

04:30.695 --> 04:32.897
